OL,8,GTwo of Aardman's finest. Nick Park's
OL,9,Gfirst outing with Wallace & Gromit
OL,10,Gsees them heading to the moon to
OL,11,Gtop-up their cheese supplies. There
OL,12,Gthey meet a little lonely robot and
OL,13,Ghelp it find happiness. And cheese.
OL,14,GFollowing that, The Wrong Trousers is
OL,15,Gour first encounter with super-villan
OL,16,GFeathers McGraw. Have you seen this
OL,17,Gchicken? Worth it for the train chase
OL,18,Galone.
